    "purpose": "Add the Simulator-owned clean-room Host Runtime adapter; make manual chat, runs, Orbit, and routines Host-only; omit the uninstalled standalone default plugin; disable Vela/AMR cloud paths; skip Cloud onboarding; lock Home and Studio to the current Simulator Workspace; hide unsupported browser, download, and community controls; close cancellation races; and approve the locked node-pty lifecycle build. No Proma code is copied."
  },
